{"tid":2017413,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［國際線］停建湄公河水壩 #StopMekongDam 聯署要人!!","createTime":"2020-05-15T05:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T20:12:01.000Z","uid":326116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dc9f7e3b757b65e74762a64953647e3802791c2a","tid":2017413,"uid":326116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:46:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">泰國手足喺Twitter戰線幫我哋，我哋冇理由唔支持返佢哋對抗中共嘅欺壓剝削！<br />\n<br />\n湄公河係東南亞多個國家嘅命脈，對於農業、工業、旅遊、食水都好重要。支共為咗發展西南地區經濟，多年嚟都策劃喺上遊起水壩。東南亞國家勢弱言輕，冇辦法阻止，大家要盡量幫忙！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">白宮聯署條link喺度：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/stop-china-build-dam-upstream-mekong-river\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fstop-china-build-dam-upstream-mekong-river&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=924915e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/stop-china-build-dam-upstream-mekong-river</a><br />\n<br />\n最後一日啦，仲爭三萬人！大家幫幫外國手足啦！</span>"},{"pid":"8b33418317b10d715c8b6cfd444020152009a50d","tid":2017413,"uid":326116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:47:24.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁照推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee382893b311ea131d69b3586321ea99e851e9ea","tid":2017413,"uid":326116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b33418317b10d715c8b6cfd444020152009a50d","tid":2017413,"uid":326116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:47:24.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁照推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:48:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">再推</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"